<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bayrom & Hugo Parfums - Perfumes de Luxo Inspirados</title>
    
    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700;900&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Dancing+Script:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <!-- AOS Animation -->
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Slick Carousel -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/slick-carousel@1.8.1/slick/slick.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/slick-carousel@1.8.1/slick/slick-theme.css">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --luxury-gold: #d4af37;
            --luxury-dark: #1a1a1a;
            --luxury-gray: #666666;
            --luxury-light: #f8f9fa;
            --luxury-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4af37, #b8941f);
            --luxury-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            color: var(--luxury-dark);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Hero Section Superior */
        .hero-superior {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2d2d2d 50%, #1a1a1a 100%);
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-superior::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 320"><path fill="%23d4af37" fill-opacity="0.1" d="M0,96L48,112C96,128,192,160,288,160C384,160,480,128,576,122.7C672,117,768,139,864,144C960,149,1056,139,1152,128C1248,117,1344,107,1392,101.3L1440,96L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path></svg>') no-repeat bottom;
            background-size: cover;
        }

        .hero-particles {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .particle {
            position: absolute;
            width: 4px;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--luxury-gold);
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0.3;
            animation: float 15s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); opacity: 0; }
            10% { opacity: 0.3; }
            90% { opacity: 0.3; }
            100% { transform: translateY(-100vh) translateX(100px); opacity: 0; }
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4af37, #ffffff, #d4af37);
            background-size: 200% auto;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            animation: shine 3s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes shine {
            to { background-position: 200% center; }
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .hero-description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            opacity: 0.8;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-hero {
            padding: 15px 40px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 500;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .btn-hero-primary {
            background: var(--luxury-gradient);
            color: white;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-hero-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-hero-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid var(--luxury-gold);
        }

        .btn-hero-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--luxury-gold);
            color: var(--luxury-dark);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        /* Seção de Estatísticas Animadas */
        .stats-superior {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #ffffff);
            position: relative;
        }

        .stat-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: var(--luxury-shadow);
            border-color: var(--luxury-gold);
        }

        .stat-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: var(--luxury-gradient);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--luxury-gold);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--luxury-gray);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Carrossel de Perfumes Premium */
        .perfumes-carousel {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: #1a1a1a;
            position: relative;
        }

        .perfume-card-premium {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d2d2d, #1a1a1a);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .perfume-card-premium::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: rotate 10s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes rotate {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .perfume-card-premium:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: var(--luxury-shadow);
            border-color: var(--luxury-gold);
        }

        .perfume-image-premium {
            width: 150px;
            height: 200px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--luxury-gold), #b8941f);
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .perfume-name-premium {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .perfume-brand-premium {
            color: var(--luxury-gold);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .perfume-price-premium {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--luxury-gold);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .perfume-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            background: var(--luxury-gradient);
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        /* Seção de Experiência Interativa */
        .experience-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #ffffff);
            position: relative;
        }

        .experience-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .experience-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: var(--luxury-shadow);
        }

        .experience-image {
            height: 250px;
            background: var(--luxury-gradient);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .experience-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .experience-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7));
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-end;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .experience-title {
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .experience-content {
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .experience-description {
            color: var(--luxury-gray);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .experience-features {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .experience-features li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            color: var(--luxury-dark);
        }

        .experience-features li:before {
            content: '✓';
            color: var(--luxury-gold);
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        /* Seção de Testemunhos Premium */
        .testimonials-superior {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: #1a1a1a;
            color: white;
        }

        .testimonial-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d2d2d, #1a1a1a);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
            position: relative;
        }

        .testimonial-quote {
            font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--luxury-gold);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .testimonial-text {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .testimonial-author {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .testimonial-role {
            color: var(--luxury-gold);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .testimonial-rating {
            color: var(--luxury-gold);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        /* Seção de CTA Superior */
        .cta-superior {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--luxury-gold), #b8941f);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .cta-superior::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2), transparent);
            animation: shimmer 3s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes shimmer {
            0% { left: -100%; }
            100% { left: 100%; }
        }

        .cta-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .cta-description {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* Footer Superior */
        .footer-superior {
            background: #0a0a0a;
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 0 30px;
        }

        .footer-brand {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--luxury-gold);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .footer-description {
            opacity: 0.8;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .footer-links {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .footer-links li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            opacity: 0.8;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: var(--luxury-gold);
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .social-icons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .social-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--luxury-gold);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .social-icon:hover {
            background: var(--luxury-gold);
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        /* Responsividade */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-title {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .hero-subtitle {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            
            .stat-number {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .cta-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .perfume-card-premium {
                margin: 10px;
            }
        }

        /* Slick Carousel Customization */
        .slick-prev, .slick-next {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background: var(--luxury-gradient);
            border-radius: 50%;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .slick-prev:before, .slick-next:before {
            color: white;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .slick-dots li button:before {
            color: var(--luxury-gold);
        }

        .slick-dots li.slick-active button:before {
            color: var(--luxury-gold);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Hero Section Superior -->
    <section class="hero-superior">
        <div class="hero-particles" id="particles"></div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content" data-aos="fade-up">
                <h1 class="hero-title">Bayrom & Hugo Parfums</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">A Redefinição do Luxo na Perfumaria</p>
                <p class="hero-description">
                    Descubra a coleção mais exclusiva de perfumes inspirados nas mais prestigiadas casas do mundo. 
                    Cada fragrância é uma obra-prima criada com matérias-primas avaliadas em até €85.000 por litro.
                </p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="#perfumes" class="btn-hero btn-hero-primary">
                        <i class="fas fa-crown me-2"></i>Explorar Coleção
                    </a>
                    <a href="#experience" class="btn-hero btn-hero-secondary">
                        <i class="fas fa-play me-2"></i>Experiência VIP
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Seção de Estatísticas Animadas -->
    <section class="stats-superior">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-gem"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-number" data-count="100">0</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Perfumes Premium</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-store"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-number" data-count="40">0</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Marcas Exclusivas</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-number" data-count="85000">0</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">€/L Valor Máximo</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-number" data-count="98">0</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">% Satisfação</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Carrossel de Perfumes Premium -->
    <section class="perfumes-carousel" id="perfumes">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
                <h2 class="display-4 text-white mb-3">Coleção Exclusiva</h2>
                <p class="lead text-white-50">As fragrâncias mais cobiçadas do mundo</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="perfumes-slider" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="perfume-card-premium">
                    <div class="perfume-badge">Mais Vendido</div>
                    <div class="perfume-image-premium">
                        <i class="fas fa-gem"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="perfume-name-premium">BP MFK Baccarat Rouge 540</h3>
                    <p class="perfume-brand-premium">Maison Francis Kurkdjian</p>
                    <div class="perfume-price-premium">R$ 300,00</div>
                    <p class="text-white-50">€80.000/L • Âmbar Gris Natural</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="perfume-card-premium">
                    <div class="perfume-badge">Exclusivo</div>
                    <div class="perfume-image-premium">
                        <i class="fas fa-crown"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="perfume-name-premium">BP Louis Vuitton Imagination</h3>
                    <p class="perfume-brand-premium">Louis Vuitton</p>
                    <div class="perfume-price-premium">R$ 320,00</div>
                    <p class="text-white-50">€85.000/L • Cactus Flower Premium</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="perfume-card-premium">
                    <div class="perfume-badge">Clássico</div>
                    <div class="perfume-image-premium">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="perfume-name-premium">BP Creed Aventus</h3>
                    <p class="perfume-brand-premium">Creed</p>
                    <div class="perfume-price-premium">R$ 220,00</div>
                    <p class="text-white-50">€50.000/L • Maçã Preta Premium</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="perfume-card-premium">
                    <div class="perfume-badge">Sensual</div>
                    <div class="perfume-image-premium">
                        <i class="fas fa-fire"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="perfume-name-premium">BP Tom Ford Black Orchid</h3>
                    <p class="perfume-brand-premium">Tom Ford</p>
                    <div class="perfume-price-premium">R$ 200,00</div>
                    <p class="text-white-50">€55.000/L • Orquídea Negra Rara</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="perfume-card-premium">
                    <div class="perfume-badge">Elegante</div>
                    <div class="perfume-image-premium">
                        <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="perfume-name-premium">BP Chanel No. 5</h3>
                    <p class="perfume-brand-premium">Chanel</p>
                    <div class="perfume-price-premium">R$ 180,00</div>
                    <p class="text-white-50">€35.000/L • Jasmim Grasse</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Seção de Experiência Interativa -->
    <section class="experience-section" id="experience">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
                <h2 class="display-4 mb-3">Experiência Bayrom & Hugo</h2>
                <p class="lead text-muted">Mais do que perfumes, uma obra de arte</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="experience-card">
                        <div class="experience-image">
                            <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/luxury1/400/250" alt="Matérias-primas">
                            <div class="experience-overlay">
                                <h3 class="experience-title">Matérias-primas Milionárias</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="experience-content">
                            <p class="experience-description">
                                Utilizamos apenas as essências mais raras do mundo, 
                                com valores de mercado de até €85.000 por litro.
                            </p>
                            <ul class="experience-features">
                                <li>Âmbar Gris Natural €35.000/kg</li>
                                <li>Açafrão Iraniano €40.000/kg</li>
                                <li>Orquídea Negra €25.000/kg</li>
                                <li>Jasmim Grasse €15.000/kg</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="experience-card">
                        <div class="experience-image">
                            <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/luxury2/400/250" alt="Perfumistas">
                            <div class="experience-overlay">
                                <h3 class="experience-title">Perfumistas Mestres</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="experience-content">
                            <p class="experience-description">
                                Nossa equipe de perfumistas renomados mundialmente 
                                cria cada fragrância como uma obra-prima única.
                            </p>
                            <ul class="experience-features">
                                <li>30+ anos de experiência</li>
                                <li>Formação em Grasse, França</li>
                                <li>Premiados internacionalmente</li>
                                <li>Exclusividade garantida</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
